Mizon Orga-Real Barrier Cream🌱

Our Mizon Multi-Cream has been formulated with natural ingredients harvested on clean areas for more than 3 years. 

💧Orga-Real Barrier Cream provides moisture all year round, specially during all season.
 
Designed to match all skin types especially sensitive skin. 

A mixture of Green Tea extract and Shea butter that provides intensive moisture and soothing. 

The more you use it, the more you will fall in love with it!❤️

Return your skin vitality and natural glow with our high-quality Rose Quartz MIZON FACIAL MASSAGE ROLLER AND GUASHA SET! 🙌🏻

✔️ Dual-sided Facial Roller to gently massage your eye area, cheeks and forehead, helping to decrease pufiness and the appearance of wrinkles! 
✔️ Guasha tool to cover larger areas such as neck and jawline, improving blood circulation and making your skin look brighter and firm!
✔️ Help your skin to evenly absorb your favorite skincare product and get a fresh and luminous skin look!

1. Refrigerate the tools for 10-30 minutes before use to increase cooling sensation!
2. Gently massage your skin with outwards movements to improve lymphatic drainage!

💧🌿 3,100ppm of our MIZON exclusive CICALURONIC-COMPLEX to soothe and intensively moisturize your skin with 7 types of Centella Asiatica extract and Hyaluronic Acid!
✅️ Vegan and cruelty free formulation!

After a long day or when your skin feels dry & irritated, give your skin a powerful boost of hydration and calming with our CICALURONIC WATER FIT MASK!

latestIgtvVideos.title: NEW FORMULATION OF MIZON ONE STEP CLEANSING WATER
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
‼️Attention! Attention! ‼️It is not dust! Is just a chemical reaction! ☝🏻

✅ We have a new formulation for our Mizon One Step Cleansing Water!
✅ Our new probiotics, plant extracts and cleansing agent ingredients interact inside of the bottle creating small black particles!
✅ The particles are not dust and are absolutely non-harmful!

Check the new properties of our new One Step Cleansing Water:

✔ 2x more humectant ingredients -> Give a smoother skin texture after cleansing
✔ 2x more fermented and naturally-derivated plant extracts -> Improve oil-water balance of your skin and repairs damaged skin barrier
✔ 1.8x more cleansing agent concentration -> Easily remove heavy make up
✔ No more stinging eye feeling! -> Relax! Now you can remove eye make up without burning feeling!

*Remove heavy make-up and impurities easily with our new Mizon One Step Cleansing Water
*Our product is dermatologically tested and suitable for all skin types!
